content.value:
"I'm okay" means I'm tired but I can handle

"I'm tired" it means "I don't have the energy to feed myself or do basic tasks"

"I'm exhausted" means "I'm so tired I probably cannot speak, move or function right now"

I don't think it's the same for non-AuDHDers. I might be wrong.
